## Operational workflow

| Cadence | Activity |
|---|---|
| Daily | Daily note under `{{DIGESTS_DIR}}/YYYY/MM/`; update the current-focus note if priority #1 changed |
| Weekly | Lint + digest (autonomous) + process Inbox when it grows past ~10 notes |
| Ad hoc | Big decision -> `{{DECISIONS_DIR}}/`; substantial AI conversation -> distill into a note |
| Monthly | Review the identity note / goals |

